# Generated deck outputs — deck.html + print.html + deck-data.json + cross-router-report.pdf,
# rebuilt from the tracked source (deck-shell.html / print-shell.html / deck-config.js /
# deck-render.js) via deck-extract → build-deck → render-pdf. Kept in deck/out/ so the tracked
# source and the gitignored generated artifacts don't share a directory. CI uploads them as the
# Pages/artifact snapshot; locally they're an untracked report (results/ is gitignored too, so
# there is no committed data to build a fresh-clone deck from — by design).
cross-router/deck/out/
